ked_by":0,"blocking":0,"total_blocking":0},"body":"### Bug description\n\nHere's a typical example of W0120 being raised:\r\n\r\n```python\r\ndef f():\r\n    while True:\r\n        if condition:\r\n            pass\r\n    else:\r\n        pass\r\n```\r\n\r\nAnd this code **doesn't** raise W0120 (correctly):\r\n\r\n```python\r\ndef f():\r\n    while True:\r\n        if condition:\r\n            break\r\n    else:\r\n        pass\r\n```\r\n\r\nBut, this code is pretty much identical in function and it **does** raise W0120 (bug):\r\n\r\n```python\r\ndef f():\r\n    while True:\r\n        if condition:\r\n            return\r\n    else:\r\n        pass\r\n```\r\n\r\nThe check for W0120 should check for both `break` and `return` in the while block.\n\n### Configuration\n\n_No response_\n\n### Command used\n\n```shell\npylint mytest.py\n```\n\n\n### Pylint output\n\n```shell\n************* Module mytest\r\nmytest.py:5:4: W0120: Else clause on loop without a break statement (useless-else-on-loop)\n```\n\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nIssue not raised\n\n### Pylint version\n\n```shell\npylint 2.11.1\r\nastroid 2.8.6-dev0\r\nPython 3.10.0 (default, Oct 13 2021, 06:45:00) [Clang 13.0.0 (clang-1300.0.29.3)]\n```\n\n\n### OS / Environment\n\n_No response_\n\n### Additional dependencies\n\n_No response_","closed_by":{"login":"Pierre-Sassoulas","id":5493666,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjU0OTM2NjY=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/5493666?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/Pierre-Sassoulas","html_url":"https://github.com/Pierre-Sassoulas","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Pierre-Sassoulas/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Pierre-Sassoulas/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Pierre-Sassoulas/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Pierre-Sassoulas/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Pierre-Sassoulas/subscriptions","organization